sequenceDiagram
    participant K8s as K8s API Server
    participant Webhook as /mutate Endpoint
    participant Handler as Handler
    participant Injector as Injector
    K8s->>Webhook: AdmissionReview(Pod CREATE)
    Webhook->>Handler: Mutate(review)
    Handler->>Handler: Parse and validate admission request
    alt norviq=enabled and no sidecar
      Handler->>Injector: CreatePatch(pod, agentClass)
      Injector-->>Handler: JSONPatch bytes
      Handler-->>Webhook: AdmissionReview(Allowed + Patch)
      Webhook-->>K8s: AdmissionReview response
      Note over K8s: Pod admitted with norviq-sidecar
    else no label or sidecar already present
      Webhook-->>K8s: Allowed (no mutation)
    end
    participant Entry as sidecar.__main__
    participant Proxy as SidecarProxy (Unix socket)
    participant HTTP as HTTP fallback (:8282)
    Entry->>Proxy: start()
    Entry->>HTTP: create_http_fallback + uvicorn.serve()
    K8s->>HTTP: GET /healthz
    HTTP-->>K8s: 200 {"status":"ok"}
